snippet.title: Zulm Ki Hukumat (1992) (HD) | Dharmendra | Govinda | Kimi Katkar | Paresh Rawal - Hit Hindi Movie
snippet.description:
"Pitamber Kohli and his two brothers, Yeshwant and Pratap get in the bad books of an underworld don named Swami, who soon launche a vendetta against them. In this goofed up situation, Pitamber gets killed, and both Yeshwant and Pratap swear to avenge his death. Pratap joins the police force, and steps up his efforts to nab Swami at any cost. Swami makes it a point to kidnap Pratap's sister and brother in law and held at gunpoint. Yeshwant goes to rescue them at the cost of his own life. Will Pratap manage to take his revenge? 

YOR - 1992
Star Cast - Govinda, Kimi Katkar, Dharmendra, Moushumi Chaterjee, Shakti Kapoor, Archana Puran Singh, Paresh Rawal, Raza Murad
Director - Bharat Rangachari
Producer – Sajid Nadiadwala
Cinematographer - Nirmal Jani
Music Director – Dilip Sen Sameer Sen
Lyricist – Sameer
Writer - Faiz-Saleem, Anees Bazmee
Editor - Deepak Wirkud, M. D. Worlikar
